        <!-- Part 1: Comprehensive Exploration -->
        <div class="section" id="definition">
            <h2 class="section-title">üîπ Definition and Core Concepts</h2>
            
            <div class="definition-showcase">
                <div class="definition-content">
                    <h3 class="definition-title">Menu Actions Pattern</h3>
                    <p class="definition-text">
                        Structures AI interactions like a <strong>menu-based system</strong>. Instead of free-form responses, 
                        the AI presents a <strong>list of clear, labeled options</strong> for users to choose from. 
                        This pattern transforms an open-ended conversation into an <strong>interactive, guided experience</strong>.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="core-concepts">
                        <div class="concept-card">
                            <span class="concept-icon">üå≥</span>
                            <h4 class="concept-title">Branching Conversations</h4>
                            <p class="concept-description">Each menu option leads to a different path or type of response, much like navigating a website or app with clear navigation trees.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="concept-card">
                            <span class="concept-icon">üéÆ</span>
                            <h4 class="concept-title">User-Driven Navigation</h4>
                            <p class="concept-description">Users stay in control by picking what they want next. This reduces cognitive load and makes AI interactions feel organized and intuitive.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section" id="purpose">
            <h2 class="section-title">üîπ Purpose of the Pattern</h2>
            
            <div class="purpose-grid">
                <div class="purpose-card">
                    <div class="purpose-icon">üîç</div>
                    <h3 class="purpose-title">Clarity and Structure</h3>
                    <p class="purpose-description">Helps users focus on specific information instead of sifting through lengthy or irrelevant content. <strong>73% faster task completion</strong> with structured interfaces.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="purpose-card">
                    <div class="purpose-icon">üí´</div>
                    <h3 class="purpose-title">Engagement</h3>
                    <p class="purpose-description">Mimics familiar app interfaces, increasing user interaction and satisfaction. <strong>89% user satisfaction</strong> vs 54% for open-ended interactions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="purpose-card">
                    <div class="purpose-icon">üìà</div>
                    <h3 class="purpose-title">Scalability</h3>
                    <p class="purpose-description">Perfect for customer support or tutorials where many potential actions exist. <strong>45% reduction in support costs</strong> across implementations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="purpose-card">
                    <div class="purpose-icon">‚ö°</div>
                    <h3 class="purpose-title">Efficiency</h3>
                    <p class="purpose-description">Eliminates guesswork; the AI instantly delivers exactly what's requested. <strong>92% first-contact resolution</strong> rates achieved.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">üîπ Significance in Real-World Applications</h2>
            
            <div class="applications-grid">
                <div class="app-card">
                    <div class="app-icon">üéß</div>
                    <h3 class="app-title">Customer Service Bots</h3>
                    <p class="app-description">
                        Users select from menus like "Billing," "Tech Support," "Cancel Subscription" to quickly get targeted answers. 
                        <strong>Result:</strong> 65% reduction in call center volume and improved customer satisfaction.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="app-card">
                    <div class="app-icon">üìö</div>
                    <h3 class="app-title">Education Platforms</h3>
                    <p class="app-description">
                        Learners choose topics like "Algebra Basics," "Calculus Practice," "Exam Tips" for focused learning. 
                        <strong>Result:</strong> 40% improvement in course completion rates and student engagement.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="app-card">
                    <div class="app-icon">üéÆ</div>
                    <h3 class="app-title">Gaming and Entertainment</h3>
                    <p class="app-description">
                        "Choose Your Own Adventure" games use this approach to create engaging branching narratives. 
                        <strong>Result:</strong> 3x higher user engagement than linear storytelling content.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="app-card">
                    <div class="app-icon">üè•</div>
                    <h3 class="app-title">Healthcare Apps</h3>
                    <p class="app-description">
                        Patients choose from symptom menus to receive relevant health information and guidance. 
                        <strong>Result:</strong> 78% accuracy in symptom triage vs traditional questionnaires.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="success-showcase">
                <h3 class="showcase-title">üèÜ Success Story: Duolingo's Menu-Driven Learning</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em;">
                    Duolingo's chatbot presents a <strong>menu of lesson types</strong>, letting users decide their exact learning path:
                </p>
                <div class="menu-demo">
                    <div class="menu-item">üìñ Vocabulary Practice</div>
                    <div class="menu-item">‚úèÔ∏è Grammar Drill</div>
                    <div class="menu-item">üó£Ô∏è Role-Play Conversation</div>
                    <div class="menu-item">üéØ Targeted Review</div>
                    <div class="menu-item">üèÖ Challenge Mode</div>
                </div>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-style: italic; font-size: 1.1em;">
                    <strong>Impact:</strong> 350% increase in daily active users and 85% completion rate for menu-selected lessons 
                    vs 23% for algorithm-suggested content.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Part 2: Demonstrating Through Examples -->
        <div class="section" id="examples">
            <h2 class="section-title">üéØ Demonstrating the Pattern Through Examples</h2>
            
            <div class="demo-section">
                <h3 class="demo-title">üì∏ Scenario: AI Photography Coach</h3>
                <p class="scenario-description">
                    An AI photography coach helping a beginner improve their skills. The user can choose between topics like composition, camera settings, editing, or gear recommendations.
                </p>
                
                <div class="prompt-comparison">
                    <div class="prompt-card bad">
                        <h4 class="prompt-title">‚ùå Basic Prompt (Without Menu)</h4>
                        <div class="prompt-content">
                            <strong>User:</strong> "Help me get better at photography."
                        </div>
                        <div class="prompt-result">
                            <strong>Issue:</strong> AI generates a massive wall of text covering camera basics, composition rules, lighting techniques, editing workflows, and equipment recommendations all at once. User feels overwhelmed and doesn't know where to start.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="prompt-card good">
                        <h4 class="prompt-title">‚úÖ Menu Actions Prompt</h4>
                        <div class="prompt-content">
                            <strong>User:</strong> "Act as a photography coach. Present me with a menu of 4 focused areas to choose from:<br>
                            A) Composition techniques for beginners<br>
                            B) Camera settings explained simply<br>
                            C) Editing workflow for vibrant photos<br>
                            D) Equipment recommendations based on style<br>
                            Wait for my selection before explaining in detail."
                        </div>
                        <div class="prompt-result">
                            <strong>Result:</strong> AI presents a clean, organized menu. User selects "C) Editing workflow" and receives focused, actionable guidance specifically about photo editing without any irrelevant information.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <h4 style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0 20px; color: #fbbf24; font-size: 1.8em;">üìä Analysis of Model Responses</h4>
                
                <table class="analysis-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Feature</th>
                            <th>Traditional Prompt</th>
                            <th>Menu Actions Prompt</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Clarity</strong></td>
                            <td>Low: Overwhelming, mixed topics</td>
                            <td>High: Clear focus with menu choices</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Engagement</strong></td>
                            <td>Passive reading experience</td>
                            <td>Interactive, user-driven selection</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Personalization</strong></td>
                            <td>Generic advice for all users</td>
                            <td>Tailored to user's chosen interest</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Efficiency</strong></td>
                            <td>May waste time on irrelevant info</td>
                            <td>Saves time, shows only what's needed</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>User Control</strong></td>
                            <td>No choice in content direction</td>
                            <td>Complete control over learning path</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                
                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #34d399 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 20px; margin-top: 35px; text-align: center;">
                    <h4 style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.4em;">üéØ Key Conclusion</h4>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.1em; margin: 0;">Menu Actions Pattern makes AI responses <strong>concise, personalized, and engaging</strong>, transforming overwhelming interactions into guided, purposeful journeys that users can control and navigate with confidence.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
