        <div style="text-align: center; padding: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9), rgba(30, 27, 75, 0.9)); border-radius: 25px; margin-top: 50px;">
            <h2 style="color: #fbbf24; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 2.2em;">üéØ Assignment Complete!</h2>
