                    ‚úÖ <strong>Creative Formats</strong>
                </div>
                <div style="background: rgba(245, 101, 101, 0.3); padding: 15px 25px; border-radius: 20px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px);">
                    ‚úÖ <strong>Interactive Assessment</strong>
                </div>
